The cops were making it difficult to get near them to shoot so there was no danger to my safety just my photography. Fortunately they stopped up the road and climbed out for a chat. Unfortunately it was for two minutes before they had to leave and those fleeting moments were interrupted by a drunk. I'll keep looking for farmers to interview, I mean no farmers no food right?? If we don't stop going to the supermarkets so much and support local farm farmers and set up our own growing communities, we're going to become soy-boy, soylent green infused, misbegotten skinny wretches that make Dylan Mulvaney look fat. I don't think we should go that way. Download my evolving health guide below and consider a donation to my crowdfunder. I'm trying to raise funds for Lymes disease, SIBO and adrenal fatigue treatments in Germany. I'm in danger of losing my speech. I'll be telling my story on a new channel soon. Thank you!!! https://www.dropbox.com/scl/fi/4fq9dt0ypr28ryzm27fg5/SIBO-A-SURVIVAL-GUIDE-BY-JONNY-STONE-BRENNAN-FOR-THE-DIRECTORS-GUT.pdf?rlkey=2fdrynrxm4y0qd9dn5thvvqoc&dl=0 DONATIONS: https://gogetfunding.com/save-my-speech/ #nofarmersnofood #nofarmersnofoodnofuture #nofarmernofood #farmersprotest #farmers #london #londonlife #londonprotest #westminster #food #foodsecurity #shoplocal #britishfarming #britishagriculture #enoughisenough #interview #police #tractors

The barber always would tell his new customers when seeing the boy approaching, ‚Äú this boy has no concept of money, watch and I‚Äôll show you.‚Äù The barber placed $1 in one hand and 2 quarters in the other hand asking the boy, ‚Äúwhich hand do you want ?‚Äù The boy chose the 2 quarters and left. The barber said, ‚Äúsee I told you !‚Äù When the man left the shop he noticed the boy leaving the ice cream shop licking his ice cream cone and walked up to the boy asking, ‚Äúwhy did you take the quarters instead of the dollar?‚Äù The boy replied, ‚Äú once I take the dollar the game ends!‚Äù

url_title: The Empire of Lies: Conscripted At Birth 6th Generational Warfare
url_description: News Fist: https://www.newsfist.net Lind - 4th Gen war: http://www.da-ic.org/5gen/2016/07/26/william-s-lind-understanding-fourth-generation-war/ ‚ÄúThe very 'rules of war' have changed. The role of nonmilitary means of achieving political and strategic goals has grown, and, in many cases, they have exceeded the power of force of weapons in their effectiveness. ‚Ä¶ All this is supplemented by *military means of a concealed character*.‚Äù - Valery Gerasimov https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Valery_Gerasimov 4th Gen Warfare: https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Fourth-generation_warfare Fourth-generation warfare (**4GW**) is [conflict](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/War) characterized by a blurring of the distinction between [war](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/War) and [politics](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Politics), and of the distinction between [combatants](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Combatants) and [civilians](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Civilians). The term was first used in 1980 by a team of [United States](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/United_States) analysts, including [William S. Lind](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/William_S._Lind), to describe [warfare](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/War)'s return to a [decentralized](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Decentralized) form. In terms of [generational modern warfare](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Generational_modern_warfare), the fourth generation signifies the [nation states](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Nation_state)' loss of their near-monopoly on combat forces, returning to modes of conflict common in pre-modern times. The simplest definition includes any war in which one of the major participants is not a [state](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sovereign_state) but rather a [violent non-state actor](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Violent_non-state_actor). Classical examples of this type of conflict, such as the [slave uprising under Spartacus](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Third_Servile_War), predate the modern concept of warfare. Fifth-generation warfare (5GW) is warfare that is conducted primarily through [non-kinetic military action](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kinetic_military_action), such as [social engineering](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Social_engineering_(political_science)), [misinformation](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Misinformation), [cyberattacks](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Cyberattack), along with emerging technologies such as [artificial intelligence](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Artificial_intelligence) and fully [autonomous systems](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Autonomous_robot). Fifth generation warfare has been described by Daniel Abbot as a war of "information and perception".[[1]](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Fifth-generation_warfare#cite_note-1) There is no widely agreed upon definition of fifth-generation warfare,[[2]](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Fifth-generation_warfare#cite_note-2) and it has been rejected by some scholars, including [William S. Lind](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/William_S._Lind), who was one of the original theorists of [fourth-generation warfare](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Fourth-generation_warfare).[[3]](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Fifth-generation_warfare#cite_note-3) -- Odysee: https://odysee.com/@Yizz_the_Eunuch:e Rumble: https://rumble.com/c/YizztheEunuch Substack: Substack: https://yizztheeunuch.substack.com/ Intro & elements by Lomax Designs: https://youtu.be/fygRHrWzXZk My content is ad-free and unsponsored except by viewers like you. You know whats awesome? SABOT rounds. You know whats even better? SABOT rounds for your rifle. Known as accelerator rounds, you too can enjoy the high velocity action of tank main guns & M2 machine guns (SLAP rounds are legit check'em out) in your own blaster. For example, you can seat a 5.56 projectile inside of a SABOT cup and load that into a .30 caliber cartridge, giving you an absurd velocity & some great effects on target. There are some special considerations like you cannot use a suppressor or muzzle device due to the SABOT cup separation once the projectile leaves the barrel (I might be wrong on that but thats how main gun SABOTs work and I'm not risking obstructing the muzzle), or that due to the nature of SABOTs there will not be any rifling pattern on the projectile. It's a very interesting tool for the toolbox and something worth looking into if your looking for some cool gat stuff.
